IDEA:
------------
- running constantly in the background, awaiting PlaybackState = 'Playing'
- ONCE PLAYBACK IS DETECTED:
    - poll track position once
    - then start incrementing timer
      (idea) poll every x seconds and correct timer accordingly (only if it is needed)
    - timer needs to take into account: Playback speed, Skipping around, pausing and track switch
    - updating the timer state should happen on recieved signals (not every x seconds if possible)

    - poll metadata once and extract file URI
    - find according (e)lrc file
    - parse
    - sync with timer

- OPTIONAL:
    - some widget implementation
    - "now playing" screen with album art and playback control


